snippet.title: Beach Invasion 1945 - Pacific: Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2390480/Beach_Invasion_1945__Pacific
Beach Invasion 1945-Pacific is a WWII shooter/tower defense game.
Defend the fortified beach against invading forces who will attack with you troops, tanks, planes and more!
